snippet: San Antonio Republicans got what they wanted, a replacement for their longtime state senator. Donna Campbell is a bona fide anti-establishment Tea Party candidate, but she lives in New Braunfels.
lead_paragraph: San Antonio Republicans got what they wanted, a replacement for their longtime state senator. Donna Campbell is a bona fide anti-establishment Tea Party candidate, but she lives in New Braunfels.
